She coughed and looked up at Atma, "I need to you do me a great 
favor.  Please, find. "coughs," find us a place for the night.  
Someplace dry and out of the way.  We will need a place to rest and 
regroup for the night.  Please Atma,  I,"coughs," I need you to do 
this. " She then lowered her head and just tried to breath.  Her ribs 
hurt and she was finding it more and more difficult just breathing.
